Available Packages
Name       : pidgin
Arch       : i386
Version    : 2.6.5
Release    : 1.el5
Size       : 1.5 M
Repo       : updates
Summary    : A Gtk+ based multiprotocol instant messaging client
URL        : http://pidgin.im/
License    : GPLv2+ and GPLv2 and MIT
Description: Pidgin allows you to talk to anyone using a variety of messaging
           : protocols including AIM, MSN, Yahoo!, Jabber, Bonjour, Gadu-Gadu,
           : ICQ, IRC, Novell Groupwise, QQ, Lotus Sametime, SILC, Simple and
           : Zephyr.  These protocols are implemented using a modular, easy to
           : use design.  To use a protocol, just add an account using the
           : account editor.
           : 
           : Pidgin supports many common features of other clients, as well as
           : many unique features, such as perl scripting, TCL scripting and C
           : plugins.
           : 
           : Pidgin is not affiliated with or endorsed by America Online, Inc.,
           : Microsoft Corporation, Yahoo! Inc., or ICQ Inc.

